div.div: Raised to kill like a pack of loyal hounds, the Baskerville children took countless lives as a band of fearsome assassins. Despite being the shunned illegitimate son of the brood, Vikir served his family faithfully, only to meet his untimely demise at his fathers hands. But when he is inexplicably reborn with a second chance at life, Vikir, armed with the memories and knowledge of his past, swears to rise above the pack and take his revenge. This time, he's ready to bite the hand that feeds. (Source: Tapas)

"A tsundere chairwoman, a demure secretary, a black diamond of a South African princess, a unique female bodyguard, and a carrot-eating, somewhat typical, bishounen - how will these people fall in love? Whether it was fate inevitable or the heart's machinations, if you meet with the Godly Expert, you will experience a one-of-a-kind apprentice life." (Source: QQ, translated)
